Installing Vim Plugins
======================
*  vim plugins can be installed (unzipped, untarred, etc.) directly into 
vim/bundle/{plugin}. For vim plugins that are on github:

dotfiles$ git submodule add http://github.com/{user}/{plugin}.git vim/bundle/{plugin}
dotfiles$ git submodule init
...
dotfiles$ git submodule update # update git-backed plugins

* To add plugin help - :helptags {plugin}/doc

Customization
=============

* irb  - add Ruby files to $HOME/.irb
* $PS1 - add $HOME/.ps1 with "export PS1=<your custom prompt>"
* EC2
* S3
